24
00:01:19,579 --> 00:01:20,997
Theo!

25
00:01:21,706 --> 00:01:23,750
Orada ne yapıyorsun?

26
00:01:23,833 --> 00:01:25,960
Buraya gel.

27
00:01:35,387 --> 00:01:37,430
Keşke bunu duyabilseydin.

28
00:01:37,931 --> 00:01:39,933
